text: The abbreviation MNU may refer to: * Matariki Network of Universities, an international group * MidAmerica Nazarene University, Olathe, Kansas, US * The Maldives National University, Male' * Mokpo National University, Muan/Mokpo, South Jeolla province, South Korea * Mianyang Normal University, Mianyang, Sichuan, China * Multi-National United, in the film District 9
title: MNU
